Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just steal the test from my desk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How mean!{/cruel/rude} \NTo call me a thief, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru brought a girl to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's tricking you!{/it's not like that}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD DAMMIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How much of a brute must you be \Nto bring an innocent girl to tears?{/What a brute/barbarian man must be \Nto bring an innocent girl to tears?}{really unsure about kaiwai, most probably kawai because vicinity/neighborhood doesn't fit here} {Yume: "kayowai onnanoko wo nakaseru nante, nante yaban na otoko nanda" -> lib. "You swine! How dare you bring an innocent girl to tears?!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm struggling to believe my eyes!{/I can't believe it}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Iyona-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, you are misled!{/wrong/mistaken}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I got carried away{/it was not kind/I mistreated you}. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? \NMaking me come all the way here...{/calling me out to such a place}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a thing for Kawai Iyona, don't you?{/you like ..., right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,N-n-no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Then I'm razing your love to the ground.{/crush into pieces}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so obsessed with that? {/Why do you have to be so damn mean?!} {unsure, lit is "why such thing only saying, you?" - so I think he means "why are you always trying to do that?"}
