Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No lies, just love{/it is true}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can even touch my butt as proof.{/as an evidence, touch my butt}
