Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't take my hand off!{/tear away}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun just said "Hey, I like you, lemme feel that butt, \NHE-HE!" and wouldn't let go of it ever since! Look! Look!{unsure that hehe is the best onomatopeia here, as I feel gehegehe in japanese is a low-toned imbecile laughter}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bunch of bullcrap!{/It's not like that at all!/are you kidding me}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, you shouldn't believe a word of it!{/believing won't do you good! Not with her!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, why won't you take your hand away?{/if you could let go of it with your hand...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm telling you! \NMy hand just won't go away! There, there, see?{/something is not releasing my hand}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijigawa must have glued it, I swear!{/attached with instant glue}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun is a devil, don't you think?{/is the worst, right?} \NAnd that's not nearly it, what he also said was...{/there's even more to it, aside from that...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you, Ijigawa!{no clue what 馬呆 really is}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now even Iyona-chan despises me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing pranks on each other?{shikaesu is rather "retaliate/take revenge"} \NI partake, too!{/I can also cooperate/help}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, a culprit that heinous, \Nshould be the first one in the spanking queue!{/someone this vicious needs punishment too/should be beaten}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no way! Because she's a girl, \Nthe whole class would side with her!{/she would find ally in everyone in class}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end... In the end, \Nonly I would be made into a villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She manipulates others like a seasoned actor, \Nthat'd lie without batting an eye!{/when it comes to matters concerning that field of expertise, she has a gift/is a genius with that contemptible talent}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Means you need to stay in shadows?{/so it is only good if we are not found/revealed}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet Limpy-kun.{I hope warawara means this - not rigid, jelly-like, but judging by honmaru feigning fear next, I suspect it may be a pun with something meaning "scary/dreadful"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I stick Honmaru's photo like this and... Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with that creepy laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't stand on just one...{unsure, maybe he means "one leg moved"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is doll for operating people, Limpy-kun.{/manipulating/pulling the strings} \NWith it, you take your revenge on Ijigawa.{korashimeru is rather to chastise; to punish; to discipline}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Taru!{/you did it}
