Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And my's friend - Honmaru's friend{, too}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijigawa and Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,F-ri-en-ds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. \NJust like Taru-chan said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Isn't that true, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, will you and Rui-chan start getting along now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like friends would.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you promise me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Most naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,700)}I promise too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid, splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan's not one bit disgusted with me!{/I managed to make up with ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. We're lucky, Honmaru.{/glad, aren't you}
