Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Meal time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is more important now \Nthan getting home, Taru?{道草を食う is to loiter on the way/lose road}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
