Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, you promised to Iyona.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, Iyona-chan probably wouldn't \Nmake friends with someone who's actually that rotten.{unsure, maybe "if yona-chan became friends with her, this means she is not that bad a person"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! What am I? Not a man?{/For I am a man, too!}
